    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169670/extras/f780a9a9b6f3d61dd0ac59529e583b8c.avif?t=1764788356\" width=1560 height=241 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Welcome to <strong>The</strong> <strong>Golden Caravan</strong>, kid. A place where fortunes are made, loyalties are lost, and every hand could be your last. Set in a smoky <strong>noir-inspired 1930s underworld</strong>, this joint ain’t run by mobsters... birds with sharp suits and cold hearts are the ones calling the shots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You walk the streets as <strong>Charlie Colombo</strong>, a slick pigeon with more guts than sense. When his grandfather <strong>Carlo Colombo</strong>, a respected locksmith, is kidnapped and dragged into the infamous <strong>Golden Caravan Casino</strong>, Charlie has no other choice but to step back into the world of rigged games, feathered crime lords, and debts paid in blood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169670/extras/3f95ebcd777a5642b315d00918e6c08c.poster.avif?t=1764788356\" width=1000 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169670/extras/3f95ebcd777a5642b315d00918e6c08c.webm?t=1764788356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><u>SATISFYING POKER-BASED COMBAT</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">'Round these parts, <strong>battles are fought at the Poker Table</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Play Poker Hands to deal damage, gain armor, heal up and even stun your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169670/extras/9555f5b80357349d51f2480d7ad7b33b.poster.avif?t=1764788356\" width=1000 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169670/extras/9555f5b80357349d51f2480d7ad7b33b.webm?t=1764788356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><u>GAME-CHANGING TRINKETS</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The <strong>Slots</strong> whisper promises... One pull, and you’re hooked.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Hit the <strong>Slot Machines</strong> scattered through the casino to earn <strong>Trinkets</strong> that offer unique effects and gameplay twists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169670/extras/f200913b036b1f6453b8443b46ff19c4.poster.avif?t=1764788356\" width=1000 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169670/extras/f200913b036b1f6453b8443b46ff19c4.webm?t=1764788356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><strong>ENGAGING ROGUELITE PROGRESSION</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Climb your way to the top, one favor at a time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Your <strong>Allies</strong> will give you <strong>Weapons</strong>, teach you <strong>Tricks</strong> and provide you other <strong>Permanent Upgrades</strong>... at a price.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169670/extras/7b401d45bce831b2abb33da3e054bf24.poster.avif?t=1764788356\" width=1000 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169670/extras/7b401d45bce831b2abb33da3e054bf24.webm?t=1764788356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><strong>NOIR-INSPIRED 1930s ATMOSPHERE</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Cigarette smoke, jazz in the background, neon lights flickering over rain-soaked streets… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The Golden Caravan</strong> it’s a place you enter chasing fortune… and leave only if luck still remembers your name.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169670/extras/f2867fc5774f22bd5fc7fe7f2976f878.poster.avif?t=1764788356\" width=1000 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169670/extras/f2867fc5774f22bd5fc7fe7f2976f878.webm?t=1764788356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><strong>A GAME OF PAYBACK</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Every hand hides a motive... this one’s revenge. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Find whoever kidnapped your grandfather, uncover the truth behind <strong>The Golden Caravan</strong>, and maybe… just maybe… the <strong>House</strong> won't win this time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p>",
